<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Thank You for Your Feedback</title>
  <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
  <link href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/5.3.0/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.10.0/font/bootstrap-icons.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    /* Elegant gradient background */
    body {
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #fce4e6, #f8d5d9);
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
      font-family: 'Merriweather', serif;
      margin: 0;
    }

    /* Card styling */
    .thankyou-card {
      max-width: 700px;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 60px 50px;
      border-radius: 35px;
      box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(146, 29, 33, 0.3), 0 15px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      border: 4px solid #921d21; /* Highlight color */
    }

    /* Decorative element for header */
    .thankyou-card::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      width: 100px;
      height: 10px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #d4af37, #e6c25e, #d4af37);
      border-radius: 5px;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    /* Icon styling */
    .thankyou-icon {
      font-size: 5.5em;
      color: #921d21; /* Main accent color */
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      z-index: 2;
      animation: pulse 1.5s infinite;
    }

    @keyframes pulse {
      0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); }
      50% { transform: scale(1.1); }
    }

    /* Heading styling */
    .thankyou-card h1 {
      font-size: 3em;
      color: #921d21; /* Highlight color */
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }

    /* Message text styling */
    .thankyou-card p {
      font-size: 1.2em;
      color: #555;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      z-index: 2;
    }

    /* Emphasized quote */
    .thankyou-card .quote {
      font-size: 1.5em;
      color: #921d21; /* Highlight color */
      font-weight: bold;
      font-style: italic;
      margin: 25px 0;
      z-index: 2;
    }

    /* Signature styling */
    .thankyou-card .signature {
      font-size: 1.2em;
      color: #444;
      margin-top: 30px;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-style: italic;
      z-index: 2;
    }

    /* Subtle hover effect */
    .thankyou-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      transition: transform 0.3s;
      box-shadow: 0 35px 70px rgba(146, 29, 33, 0.4), 0 20px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="thankyou-card">
    <div class="thankyou-icon">
      <i class="bi bi-chat-heart-fill"></i>
    </div>
    <h1>Thank You!</h1>
    <p>Your feedback means the world to us. We sincerely appreciate the time and effort you took to share your thoughts, helping us improve and grow.</p>
    <p class="quote">"Your insights inspire our excellence."</p>
    
  </div>

  <!-- Bootstrap Bundle with Popper -->
  <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/5.3.0/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
